{
  "/api/v2/admin/farms/{id}": {
    "put": {
      "summary": "Update farm by ID",
      "tags": ["Admin/Farms"],
      "description": "Updates a farm's information including name, address, coordinates, and associated users.\n\n## Path Parameters\n\n- **id**\n  - **Type**: Integer\n  - **Description**: Unique identifier of the farm to update\n  - **Required**: Yes\n\n## Form Fields and Validation Rules\n\n### Field Specifications\n\n- **name**\n  - **Type**: String\n  - **Length**: 3-100 characters\n  - **Validation**: Must not be empty\n  - **Purpose**: Updated name for the farm\n\n- **address**\n  - **Type**: String\n  - **Length**: 5-200 characters\n  - **Validation**: Must not be empty\n  - **Purpose**: Updated physical location of the farm\n\n- **latitude**\n  - **Type**: String (numeric value)\n  - **Range**: Must be between -90 and 90\n  - **Validation**: Must be a valid geographic coordinate\n  - **Format**: Decimal degrees (e.g., \"-1.345678\")\n\n- **longitude**\n  - **Type**: String (numeric value)\n  - **Range**: Must be between -180 and 180\n  - **Validation**: Must be a valid geographic coordinate\n  - **Format**: Decimal degrees (e.g., \"2.345678\")\n\n- **users**\n  - **Type**: Array of integers\n  - **Validation**:\n    - Must contain at least one user ID\n    - Each ID must represent an existing user in the system\n    - Each user must have the OWNER role\n  - **Behavior**: This will replace all existing user associations\n  - **Purpose**: Associates farm owners with the farm",
      "security": [
        {
          "apiKey": []
        }
      ],
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "id",
          "in": "path",
          "required": true,
          "description": "Unique identifier of the farm to update",
          "schema": {
            "type": "integer",
            "example": 1
          }
        }
      ],
      "requestBody": {
        "required": true,
        "content": {
          "application/json": {
            "schema": {
              "type": "object",
              "required": ["name", "address", "latitude", "longitude", "users"],
              "properties": {
                "name": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "Name of the farm. Required. Must be a string between 3 and 100 characters.",
                  "example": "Nuevo Nombre"
                },
                "address": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "Physical address of the farm. Required. Must be a string between 5 and 200 characters.",
                  "example": "Nueva Dirección"
                },
                "latitude": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "Latitude coordinate of the farm location. Required. Must be a valid number between -90 and 90.",
                  "example": "-1.345678"
                },
                "longitude": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "Longitude coordinate of the farm location. Required. Must be a valid number between -180 and 180.",
                  "example": "2.345678"
                },
                "users": {
                  "type": "array",
                  "description": "Array of user IDs to be associated with the farm. Required. Must contain at least one user ID. Each user ID must be a valid number, must exist in the system, and must have the OWNER role. This will replace all existing user associations.",
                  "items": {
                    "type": "integer"
                  },
                  "example": [2]
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "responses": {
        "200": {
          "description": "Farm updated successfully",
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                  "message": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "example": "Farm updated successfully"
                  },
                  "data": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
                        "id": {
                          "type": "integer",
                          "example": 1
                        },
                        "name": {
                          "type": "string",
                          "example": "Nuevo Nombre"
                        },
                        "address": {
